### Definitions

#### Scalar
- Single numerical value.

#### Vector
- Quantity with magnitude.

#### Matrix
- Two-dimensional array.

#### Tensor
- N-dimensional data structure.

### Note
- For matrix operations, NumPy arrays are preferred over Python lists.

